FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our toilet paper marketplace
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the toilet paper marketplace work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace connects toilet paper buyers with sellers. Browse listings, compare prices, and order your preferred brands with ease.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What types of toilet paper are available?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We offer a wide range of toilet paper options, including eco-friendly, luxury, budget-friendly, and bulk quantities to suit all preferences.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Sellers handle shipping. Delivery times and costs vary based on location and seller policies. You can view shipping details on each listing.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I sell toilet paper on this platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Sign up as a seller, create listings for your toilet paper products, and start selling to our community of buyers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if I'm not satisfied with my purchase?

PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Toilet Paper Marketplace
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does our toilet paper marketplace work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our marketplace connects toilet paper buyers with sellers. Users can browse various brands, compare prices, and place orders directly through our platform. Sellers can list their products and manage inventory easily.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of toilet paper are available?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We offer a wide range of toilet paper options, including eco-friendly, ultra-soft, quilted, recycled, and bulk packages. You can find products from major brands as well as smaller, boutique manufacturers.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Shipping is handled by our network of sellers. Most orders are processed within 1-2 business days. We offer various shipping options, including standard, expedited, and bulk delivery for larger orders.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if I'm not satisfied with my purchase?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We have a 30-day return policy for unopened packages. If you're unsatisfied with your purchase, contact our customer service team, and we'll guide you through the return process or help resolve any issues you may have.
